<font color="japanese">ソウ

609
00:51:49,648 --> 00:51:51,358
<font color="japanese">ソウ

610
00:51:52,943 --> 00:51:54,194
<font color="japanese">出てきて

611
00:51:55,445 --> 00:51:56,988
<font color="japanese">お願いよ

612
00:51:57,614 --> 00:51:58,490
<font color="japanese">ソウ

613
00:52:00,492 --> 00:52:01,701
<font color="japanese">ソウ

614
00:52:03,662 --> 00:52:04,788
<font color="japanese">どうしよう

615
00:52:04,871 --> 00:52:06,039
<font color="japanese">大丈夫だ

616
00:52:06,164 --> 00:52:07,958
<font color="japanese">ソウがいない

617
00:52:08,041 --> 00:52:11,169
<font color="japanese">必ず見つかるよ
落ち着いて捜そう

618
00:52:12,337 --> 00:52:13,338
<font color="japanese">大丈夫

619
00:52:25,141 --> 00:52:27,227
<font color="japanese">どうしたらいいの

620
00:52:30,981 --> 00:52:32,315
<font color="japanese">ソウ

